#: of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.PlotAccessor._gen_func.<locals>._inner:8
#: of
msgid ""
"Column in the DataFrame to group by.  .. versionchanged:: 1.4.0     "
"Previously, `by` is silently ignore and makes no groupings"
msgstr ""
"用于分组的 DataFrame 列。  .. versionchanged:: 1.4.0     之前，`by` 被"
"静默忽略并且不会进行分组"

