#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.PlotAccessor._gen_func.<locals>._inner:32
#: of
msgid ""
"When we roll a die 6000 times, we expect to get each value around 1000 "
"times. But when we roll two dice and sum the result, the distribution is "
"going to be quite different. A histogram illustrates those distributions."
msgstr ""
"当我们掷一个骰子 6000 次时，我们期望每个值大约出现 1000 次。但当我们掷"
"两个骰子并将结果相加时，分布会完全不同。直方图可以展示这些分布。"

